data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 1 and a 1/2 bath home that is easily able to convert to 2nd full bath. Open concept with large kitchen. Recent remodel includes Pergo Wood plank waterproof flooring, paint, stainless steel appliances, insulated windows and cabinets. Home is located in the College Heights subdivision with large corner lot, fully fenced back yard, mature trees and a separate storage building, with deck and Gazebo.
